&lt;a href='https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2488/auto-generate-database-diagram-mysql' target="_blank" rel="noopener">puedan&lt;/a>
&lt;a href='https://stackoverflow.com/questions/32379038/how-can-i-generate-an-entity-relationship-er-diagram-of-a-database-using-micro' target="_blank" rel="noopener">generarse a partir&lt;/a>
